(4, 'Are the colors and designs exactly as shown in the photos?', 'We try our best to ensure the photos accurately represent each product. However, due to natural lighting and handcrafted processes, slight variations in color and pattern may occurâ€”this is part of their unique charm.', '2025-05-14 11:06:04'),
(5, 'Do you ship across India?', 'Yes, we deliver across India. For specific delivery timelines, please refer to our Shipping Policy.', '2025-06-18 12:25:57');
