(1, 'Payment Policy ', '&nbsp;<b style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Payments</span></b><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">How do I make a payment for a\r\nJaipur Window purchase?</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Domestic Payments (within India)</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Jaipur Window offers multiple\r\npayment methods for customers in India, including:</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">- Credit/Debit Cards (Visa,\r\nMastercard, American Express)</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">- Net Banking</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">- E-Gift Vouchers</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">- Cash on Delivery (COD)</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Our trusted payment gateway,\r\nRazorpay, uses advanced SSL encryption technology to securely protect your card\r\ninformation.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">International Payments (outside\r\nIndia)</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">For international customers, we\r\naccept the following payment options:</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">- International Credit/Debit\r\nCards</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">- PayPal</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Razorpay\'s SSL encryption ensures\r\nthe safety of your card details during the checkout process. If you face any\r\nissues with our payment gateway, please email us at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:jaipurwindow@gmail.com\"><span style=\"color:#2698F2\">jaipurwindow@gmail.com</span></a>&nbsp;or\r\ncontact our team.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Can I pay with my international\r\ncard and get the order shipped to an Indian address?</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Yes, absolutely! Simply enter\r\nyour shipping and billing details accordingly on the checkout page and pay using\r\nyour international card. Our team will handle the rest.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Do you have Cash on Delivery\r\n(COD)?</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Yes, we offer Cash on Delivery\r\n(COD) service for orders delivered within India. This is supported by our\r\ntrusted courier partner, Delhivery Express.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">To place a COD order:</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">1. Add items to your cart and\r\nproceed to checkout.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">2. Select \"Cash on Delivery\r\n(COD)\" as the payment option.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">3. We will call you to confirm\r\nyour order.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">4. Once verified, your order will\r\nbe processed for COD delivery.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">5. Pay the delivery person in\r\ncash when you receive your parcel.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Is COD Chargeable?</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">COD is free for orders above </span><span style=\"font-family: Georgia, &quot;serif&quot;;\">â‚¹</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">500. For\r\norders below </span><span style=\"font-family: Georgia, &quot;serif&quot;;\">â‚¹</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">500, there is an additional </span><span style=\"font-family: Georgia, &quot;serif&quot;;\">â‚¹</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">50 shipping charge. Please note that\r\nCOD orders may take an extra 1-2 days for delivery </span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">compared to\r\nprepaid orders, as they require additional confirmation.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">If you would like to convert your\r\nCOD order to a prepaid order, simply reply to the order confirmation email, and\r\nwe will send you a payment link.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">How can you save time and nature\r\nby placing a Prepaid order?</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Placing a prepaid order with\r\nCredit/Debit Card or Net Banking can help speed up your delivery, as it skips\r\nthe additional confirmation step required for COD orders. This also helps us\r\nreduce paper usage, which is required for COD order processing.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Are there any hidden charges on\r\nJaipur Window?</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">No, there are absolutely no\r\nhidden charges on Jaipur Window. The prices listed for all products are final\r\nand all-inclusive, with free delivery across India.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">How do I pay using a Credit/Debit\r\ncard, and is it safe?</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">We accept all Visa, Mastercard,\r\nand American Express cards. You\'ll need to enter your 16-digit card number and\r\nthe 3-digit CVV code (found on the back of the card) to complete the payment.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">All your credit/debit card\r\ndetails remain confidential and private. Jaipur Window and our payment gateway,\r\nRazorpay, use advanced SSL encryption technology to protect your card\r\ninformation.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">If you have any further\r\nquestions, please feel free to email us at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:jaipurwindow@gmail.com\"><span style=\"color:#2698F2\">jaipurwindow@gmail.com</span></a>&nbsp;or\r\ncall us at +91-8005948153 or +91-9492932623. Our team will be happy to assist\r\nyou.</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '2025-06-15 06:37:12');
INSERT INTO `tbl_privacy_policy` (`id`, `heading`, `content`, `create_at`) VALUES
(1, 'Privacy Policy', '&nbsp;<b style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;Privacy Policy</span></b><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Commitment\r\nto Privacy<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">At\r\nJaipur Window, we are dedicated to protecting the privacy and security of your\r\npersonal information. We follow strict procedures to ensure the\r\nconfidentiality, integrity, and safety of the data stored on our systems.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Acceptance\r\nof Terms<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">By\r\naccessing or using our website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood,\r\nand agree to be bound by the terms of this Privacy Policy and our Website Terms\r\nof Use. If you do not agree to these terms, please exit the page and do not use\r\nthe website.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Secure\r\nShopping<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">To\r\nprovide a secure shopping experience, we utilize encryption technology, secure\r\ncommerce servers, and authentication methods to protect your personal\r\ninformation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Information\r\nCollection<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Before\r\ncompleting your purchase, we may request your name, phone number, email,\r\nbilling, and shipping addresses. This information, along with your payment\r\nmethod, is necessary to fulfill your order. We may share this data with\r\nspecific members of our staff and select third parties (such as our credit card\r\nprocessor and shipping provider) involved in your transaction and order\r\ndelivery.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" st