(1, 'Return Policy', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:2\"><b><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Cambria\">ðŸ“¦</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Return\r\n&amp; Exchange Policy<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">At\r\nJaipur Window, we take great pride in offering handcrafted and handwoven\r\ntreasures that reflect Indiaâ€™s rich cultural heritage.</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"> Each piece is carefully curated and\r\ninspected before dispatch. However, if for any reason you are not fully\r\nsatisfied, our return and exchange policy is designed to be transparent and\r\nsimple.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\ntext-align:center;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">\r\n\r\n</span></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><br></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Returns/Refund Exchange Policy for saree:</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Eligible for Return/Exchange:</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Genuine Quality Issues</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">: If you\r\nreceive a saree with genuine quality problems, please contact our customer\r\nsupport team within 7 days of receiving the product. We may request additional\r\nphotographs or other verification to process your return. We will initiate the\r\nrefund/exchange process once we have received the product and investigated the\r\nissue.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Damaged or Wrong/Missing Product</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">: If your\r\nsaree arrives damaged or if you receive the wrong item, please contact us\r\nwithin 7 days of receiving the product. We will initiate the refund process or\r\nsend you the correct item at no additional shipping cost, based on your\r\npreference.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Not Eligible for Return/Exchange:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">RTO (Return to Origin):</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;Customers\r\nmust provide a complete shipping address with an active phone number. If the\r\npackage is returned to our warehouse due to failed delivery attempts by the\r\nshipping agency, any reshipping requests will require the customer to pay\r\nadditional shipping charges at actual cost.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Color Mismatch:</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;We\r\ntake great care in photographing the sarees to match the true colors. However,\r\nslight color variations may occur due to differences in screen displays. Color\r\nvariation or mismatch will not be considered a valid reason for a refund.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">General Terms:</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\r\nmargin-left:15.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.