an></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Absolutely! You can easily place\r\nan order and pay with your international card, and we\'ll ship it to your Indian\r\naddress. Just fill in your shipping and billing details on the checkout page,\r\nand our team will handle the rest.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Shipping Charges</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Jaipur Window provides FREE\r\nSHIPPING across India for orders above </span><span style=\"font-family: Georgia, &quot;serif&quot;;\">â‚¹</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">500. For orders below </span><span style=\"font-family: Georgia, &quot;serif&quot;;\">â‚¹</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">500, a\r\nshipping fee o</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">f </span><span style=\"font-family: Georgia, &quot;serif&quot;;\">â‚¹</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">50 will be charged. Additionally,\r\nproducts with above-average weight may incur extra shipping charges, which will\r\nbe mentioned on the product page if applicable.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Delivery Timeline</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">We maintain 100% inventory, so\r\nyour order will be shipped within 24-48 hours of placing the order and\r\nconfirming the payment. Depending on your location, the delivery will typically\r\ntake 3-7 days after dispatch. You\'ll receive a confirmation email with tracking\r\ndetails when your order is dispatched.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Minimum Order Value</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">There is no minimum order value.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Delivery Method</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">We prefer to deliver through\r\nDelhivery. If Delhivery is unavailable in your area, we\'ll ship via Government\r\nRegistered Speedpost. If you need your order to be shipped by a specific\r\nlogistics company, please let us know.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Warranty and Hidden Costs</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">There are no extra taxes, hidden\r\ncosts, or additional shipping charges. The price mentioned on the website is\r\nthe final price, and all taxes are included.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Changing Shipping Address</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">If your order is still being\r\nprocessed and has not been dispatched, you can contact us via email at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:jaipurwindow@gmail.com\"><span style=\"color:#2698F2\">jaipurwindow@gmail.com</span></a>&nbsp;or\r\nphone at +91-8005948153 and +91-9492932623 (India &amp; International) to\r\nmodify your shipping address.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Further Assistance</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">For any special questions, please\r\nfeel free to email us at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:jaipurwindow@gmail.com\"><span style=\"color:black\">jaipurwindow@gmail.com</span></a>&nbsp;or call us at\r\n+91-8005948153 and +91-9492932623 (India &amp; International), and we\'ll be\r\nhappy to assist you.</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2025-06-15 06:52:25');
